%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b6d9004416d76c6499bb5cc8be070323, type: 3}
  m_Name: TakasuHaruko
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Takasu Haruko
  description: The first and the oldest of the Takasu sisters... by about six minutes.
    Takasu Haruko is the smartest of the triplets. Well, she isn't that smart, since
    she's one of the lower performing students of the class. But she's always trying
    to help her sisters just barely pass their exams. She's also formed a weird antagonistic
    relationship with her English teacher, since she gets bugged by her the most.
    It's hard to blame her when she's just doing everything she can to fit in.
  fullBody: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b0140d3d5845bf94ba8bfef162384a32, type: 3}
  portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 398618a7ff83bcf40aef1876ee2ae2d4, type: 3}
  relationships:
  - name: Takasu Mitsuko
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9a37b3f5fd958004bba2c106a2580af1, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 5
      comment: With a new school, I need to keep her safe so she can learn.
    - name: 50
      storyProgression: 50
      relationship: 4
      comment: She doesn't need me to watch over her as often anymore. I'll just
        continue helping her study.
    - name: 180
      storyProgression: 180
      relationship: 6
      comment: I think I should spend more time focusing on myself. She'll be fine
        on her own.
    - name: 290
      storyProgression: 290
      relationship: 5
      comment: We'll never be apart again.
  - name: Takasu Katsuko
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1069d608ddedbbe4ea26946b346e6c63, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 5
      comment: She's one of the only people by my side. I'll make sure we survive
        together.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 5
      comment: It can be frustrating looking after her, but I can't stop caring about
        her.
    - name: 160
      storyProgression: 160
      relationship: 6
      comment: She's getting in the way... She refuses to change no matter what I
        do...
    - name: 180
      storyProgression: 180
      relationship: 8
      comment: Stop clinging to me and let me enjoy myself for once! If that's how
        you want to be, then do that on your own!
    - name: 200
      storyProgression: 200
      relationship: 9
      comment: If you don't want to be around me anymore, so be it! I've been happier
        without you!
    - name: 230
      storyProgression: 230
      relationship: 6
      comment: I... I wish you were still protecting me...
    - name: 250
      storyProgression: 250
      relationship: 16
      comment: I'm alone again... I shouldn't have driven you away... I'm sorry...
    - name: 275
      storyProgression: 275
      relationship: 17
      comment: I'm sorry... It's my fault this happened... I shouldn't... I'm sorry...
    - name: 290
      storyProgression: 290
      relationship: 5
      comment: I'm by your side, Katsuko. I won't leave you alone ever again.
  - name: Takasu Yuuchi
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 55a3c7e8fa975994dab138f1804d4834, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 3
      comment: He's my baby brother! He's quite cute too.
    - name: 300
      storyProgression: 300
      relationship: 4
      comment: I think I've started to respect him more after he stepped up.
  - name: Takasu Ryuuji
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d2082e7f2c181c4479e3e99a1996ad34, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 5
      comment: He's the kindest in the world! I want to make him proud!
    - name: 180
      storyProgression: 180
      relationship: 5
      comment: He's very wise and always gives me great advice.
  - name: Takasu Taiga
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dd6c719f114c5884bad0ca2d176f1648, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 7
      comment: Can't stand her nagging...
    - name: 250
      storyProgression: 250
      relationship: 8
      comment: G-get off my shoulder and just let me do what I want!
  - name: Sagawa Kaito
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9602679b725d884db59cada9692373a, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: I didn't even know this guy was in my class.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 6
      comment: I have to work with this guy? He gives me the creeps... Well, I'll
        do my best.
    - name: 125
      storyProgression: 125
      relationship: 11
      comment: He's... actually not a bad guy. I think I like being around him.
    - name: 150
      storyProgression: 150
      relationship: 12
      comment: Maybe we can be something more?
    - name: 160
      storyProgression: 160
      relationship: 12
      comment: I never thought I'd get this close to someone... I'm happy.
    - name: 170
      storyProgression: 170
      relationship: 17
      comment: Wh... What did I do wrong?
    - name: 175
      storyProgression: 175
      relationship: 11
      comment: I won't take that answer.
    - name: 190
      storyProgression: 190
      relationship: 13
      comment: I love you, Kaito.
    - name: 210
      storyProgression: 210
      relationship: 12
      comment: I... I know I'm not the best, but I don't want to be apart again.
    - name: 230
      storyProgression: 230
      relationship: 14
      comment: We've shown each other everything... It feels like nothing can tear
        us apart.
    - name: 250
      storyProgression: 250
      relationship: 17
      comment: I'm an idiot... I didn't mean to hurt him... I was only thinking of
        myself...
    - name: 260
      storyProgression: 260
      relationship: 16
      comment: What's going to happen now? Is this really... the end?
    - name: 275
      storyProgression: 275
      relationship: 11
      comment: You'd really forgive someone like me?
    - name: 290
      storyProgression: 290
      relationship: 15
      comment: We'll be together forever!
  - name: Ninomae Arisa
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1801885d89f72374e8d8f225007555ab, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: Nothing remarkable.
    - name: 10
      storyProgression: 10
      relationship: 6
      comment: Mitsuko made a friend? I'll need to see if this lasts...
    - name: 25
      storyProgression: 25
      relationship: 1
      comment: They really are friends... It finally happened to one of us... I'll
        support her.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 2
      comment: She's quite an upstanding girl and has been quite kind to us.
  - name: Kishida Mie
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75a38326ef94e1c499364e6bea112370, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: She doesn't look like she wants to be spoken to, so I won't.
    - name: 35
      storyProgression: 35
      relationship: 1
      comment: She's Mitsuko's friend. I don't sense any bad intentions, so I'll
        be friendly for now.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 2
      comment: I ended up spending more time with her because of Mitsuko, but I don't
        really know her that well.
    - name: 160
      storyProgression: 160
      relationship: 2
      comment: Even though she's a little weird, she's nice to have around!
    - name: 280
      storyProgression: 280
      relationship: 3
      comment: She actually fought for us! I never thought she had that in her.
  - name: Koigakubo Tarou
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6b80ba0c077c73d4aa5699e5c44366b9, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: He's the homeroom teacher's son. Not much of a talker.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 6
      comment: It's messy between me and his mother... Talking to him is just awkward...
    - name: 200
      storyProgression: 200
      relationship: 1
      comment: I suppose everything's all well now. I'll be as friendly as I can.
    - name: 300
      storyProgression: 300
      relationship: 2
      comment: He was on our side in the end. I appreciate it greatly.
  - name: Takano Saki
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a197f9d1e638c64499a9da8564c2c785, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: She's looks cute, I suppose.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 1
      comment: She's been nothing but friendly, despite all the trouble my sisters
        and I give her.
    - name: 175
      storyProgression: 175
      relationship: 3
      comment: I'll always support her as Student Council President!
    - name: 280
      storyProgression: 280
      relationship: 3
      comment: After everything we've been through, it's great to know she has my
        back.
  - name: Yoshida Satoshi
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a1f794b0c2aed9d45b59d7b4572c8dfb, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: Well, he's in my class.
    - name: 25
      storyProgression: 25
      relationship: 0
      comment: At least he's easy to talk to.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 1
      comment: He's just a familiar face.
    - name: 300
      storyProgression: 300
      relationship: 2
      comment: He's been supporting us, and I'm thankful.
  - name: Kogarashi Hitomi
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fed86471980176d498fa75256439b42d, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: Hm? We haven't even met yet.
    - name: 100
      storyProgression: 100
      relationship: 0
      comment: He's pretty hot and seems friendly. We're in the same club too.
    - name: 135
      storyProgression: 135
      relationship: 2
      comment: Feels good to know him a little more.
    - name: 180
      storyProgression: 180
      relationship: 2
      comment: Ah, he's gotten close to Katsuko. How nice!
    - name: 235
      storyProgression: 235
      relationship: 6
      comment: Something's off... I can trust him, right?
    - name: 275
      storyProgression: 275
      relationship: 10
      comment: You'll be dead the next time we meet!
  - name: Koigakubo Yuri
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d411c21d515fe4a4cae0fffbbc885d31, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 0
      comment: I'll do my best.
    - name: 25
      storyProgression: 25
      relationship: 6
      comment: I keep getting into trouble...
    - name: 75
      storyProgression: 75
      relationship: 7
      comment: I'm trying as hard as I can, woman!
    - name: 150
      storyProgression: 150
      relationship: 2
      comment: I... I managed to exceed her expectations!
    - name: 200
      storyProgression: 200
      relationship: 3
      comment: I know you have my back, Yuri-sensei!
  - name: Takasu Yasuko
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 005537d58d9b8f145b2a757e4b1b5d30, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 4
      comment: She's my grandmother!
  - name: Kitamura Yuusaku
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: de13e7c31359b3641b7ba1e869733eeb, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 1
      comment: He's a funny guy that sends us gifts from America sometimes. Never
        spent a lot of time with him in person though.
  - name: Kushieda Minori
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dc268a8534575254dac472a77c2d34d6, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 1
      comment: It's been a while since we've seen each other, but she's nice from
        what I remember.
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 175
      relationship: 2
      comment: She treated us after she came back from America!
  - name: Kawashima Ami
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3c892378169223b49bb7bc0ad680814e, type: 2}
    stages:
    - name: 0
      storyProgression: 0
      relationship: 3
      comment: I love hanging out with her! She's always spoiling us...
